3.24.16 GetMaxBondIdx 
 

 
    
virtual unsigned int GetMaxBondIdx() const
    
Return a lower bond on the maximum bond index.  All bond indices
returned by OEBondBase::GetIdx on bonds belonging to this molecule are
guaranteed to be less than this value.  Obviously, the returned result
is always greater than or equal to OEMolBase::NumBonds().

  

  
          
     
        
